{"type": "article", "id": 6974, "title": "TIMBA Table 桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-02T07:39:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234151mf6H7sjP3tyeJ1Ip.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t英国设计品牌 PearsonLloyd Design 带来的这款桌子考虑的基本问题便是：在当代社会，如何解决人们围绕桌子共同工作的需求。这款桌子的桌面采用橡木结构，看上去优雅安静，桌子中间设置一个转盘，使得每个人都可以方便使用电源和网络。在获奖评语中，iF 主办方写到：这款桌子是当代办公室需求的回应，将促进办公室沟通和效率。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234149pNBASvyO2MQriJke.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234150on6U1Lv7tSjHF2pY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234150J4iTL7XDWtQMbhy9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.22222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}